{"tid":1539083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"下一次遊行如果人數太少會令好多人覺得大部分人已經袋住徹回，運動都會好快完結","createTime":"2019-09-04T08:48:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T09:02:06.000Z","uid":70205,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6f9a794342f7d9b4924a639c79e3fd10823d137e","tid":1539083,"uid":70205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:48:05.000Z","msg":"文宣一定要keep 住，要求民陣再搞遊行"},{"pid":"6416f10eb57eb4b51b08d1c626040d592866443a","tid":1539083,"uid":290815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:48:38.000Z","msg":"大家要到幾時先察覺，靠政府去實現五大訴求已經變成一個好恐怖既局？<br />\n<br />\n[時光倒流Re-post] 香港民權抗爭&mdash;&mdash;五大訴求，缺一不可？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538204\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538204</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先大家可以選擇服用咗以上文章先<br />\n<br />\n然後我可以反問一句，有冇人諗過五大訴求真係實現既情況會係點？<br />\n<br />\n係，的確可能證實到瘋狂既民意係可以改變到政府所作出既決定，但下次兩地一檢呢？再下次智慧燈柱、全面普教中呢？反送中2.0、3.0發生，真係好？點解要跟住個垃圾政權條尾走？<br />\n<br />\n香港人，唔好再「<span style=\"color: red;\">要求</span>」政府畀到五個願望你哋，請大家一齊親手達成依五個，甚至一百個願望都得，可唔可以？<br />\n<br />\n睇唔明我講咩既話請讀上面篇文章一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fbeafa6528480265cabb34faf2170359c127557","tid":1539083,"uid":70205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:53:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6824d29f7e9e57b68eb8e2ff36a36a9e4624d6e0","tid":1539083,"uid":76705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:54:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n9月8日 下午2點 <br />\n香港人權及民主法 <br />\n美國領使館<br />\n不見不散</div></strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"dada93ba08759d0aac179600138ff024e20cd717","tid":1539083,"uid":70205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:58:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3b302fd40a1635136431977c9ad6c7d8bace5476","tid":1539083,"uid":211578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T09:00:38.000Z","msg":"6月9撤回同9月4撤回分別係邊呀?<br />\n<br />\n分別在於:<br />\n3隻眼<br />\n2次地鐵恐襲<br />\n2人被刀手斬至重傷<br />\n8人離世<br />\n超過100人被檢控<br />\n超過1000人被捕<br />\n受傷, 逃亡不計其數<br />\n<br />\n淨係計以上的分別, 已經好明顯。<br />\n還有整個警隊及制度的不公義已暴露。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OkC3deC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOkC3deC.jpg&h=34367fd0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"27a8061f4691c297c9c2d4f3a28f7c78d9ae2a79","tid":1539083,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T09:01:50.000Z","msg":"呢個禮拜活動照舊<br />\n宣傳下先<br />\n再等民陣籌備搞大遊行"},{"pid":"f7badb69b6e127c6ccf4aab90ed886980fbfb278","tid":1539083,"uid":270571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T09:02:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3xpQCyn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3xpQCyn.png&h=6ef58af4&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}